 in the deeply human relationship with material sustenance.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aFood habits in literature. 0aFood in literature. 0aItalian poetryxHistory and criticismyTo 1400. 4aCultural Studies. 4aEarly Modern Studies. 4aFood Studies. 4aHistory, Art History, and Archaeology. 4aLiterary Theory, Criticism, and History. 4aMedieval Studies. 7aHISTORY / Europe / Italy.2bisacsh  aDante, food, medieval, literature.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAmsterdam University Press Complete eBook-Package 2022z978311076709408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2022 Part 2z978311076700108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishz978311099389908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022z9783110994810oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2022 Englishz978311099296008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2022z9783110992939oZDB-23-DEG40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9789048550036?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9789048550036423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9789048550036/original  a978-3-11-076700-1  DG Plus PP Package 2022 Part 2b2022  a978-3-11-076709-4  Amsterdam University Press Complete eBook-Package 2022b2022  a978-3-11-099296-0  EBOOK PACKAGE History 2022 Englishb2022  a978-3-11-099389-9  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishb2022  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_HICS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DEGb2022  aZDB-23-DGGb2022